ChangeList.Description: Added the [Release](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/noncustodialDataSource-Release?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [noncustodialDataSource](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/noncustodialDataSource?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [UpdateIndex](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/noncustodialDataSource-UpdateIndex?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [noncustodialDataSource](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/noncustodialDataSource?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Changed the type of the **bindingParameter** parameter in the [release](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/noncustodialDataSource-release?view=graph-rest-beta) method.
Changed the type of the **bindingParameter** parameter in the [updateIndex](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/noncustodialDataSource-updateIndex?view=graph-rest-beta) method.
